name: Nothing but thieves
description: This piece of mine is taken from my trip to the vinyl shop. Vinyl stores are an example of originality where we can buy original works. But, isn't something original easy to steal and imitate? Like a country that is not recognized which will then be stolen by a more powerful country. Maybe that's an exaggerated analogy, but isn't the phenomenon of piracy of a work already rampant and can't be stopped? Therefore, in this work, I will speak about the rejection of piracy of a work
